{"tid":1092520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"婦產科名醫被爆門診挑「處女」 美女音樂家老婆抓姦","createTime":"2019-04-05T02:05:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T03:00:10.000Z","uid":8131,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"df65c69d7e7cbd3105fe400a41c181cbb6ef593e","tid":1092520,"uid":8131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:05:28.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕苗栗一間大型醫院一名婦產科名醫，被爆利用內診時物色處女病患，並展開追求，他的妻子上月在台南一間旅館抓姦，名醫和小三被依妨害家庭的現行犯身分帶到派出所，名醫並當場簽下離婚協議書，和妻子和解，與小三脫身後，沒移送法辦。<br />\n《鏡週刊》報導，這名婦產科名醫32歲，身高約180公分，斯文帥氣很有異性緣，原在台中一間知名醫院任職，去年底被高薪挖到苗栗。名醫的妻子為留學德國的音樂家，曾加入柏林愛樂交響樂團，她放棄高薪回台，與名醫育有2名子女，也兼當音樂家教。<br />\n報導提到，名醫妻子自爆，老公以前常要求她開腿、看她下體，甚至聞氣味，她生完小孩後，老公就不碰她，還自己跑去結紮，後來更不接手機搞失蹤，車上留有別人的長髮，她因此懷疑老公有小三。<br />\n今年3月，她透過律師安排跟監，拍到老公與小三約會，還跟小四去開房間。名醫妻子抓到老公外遇當場大罵「自己的病人也敢上！」「說什麼開年會，結果是開房間。」也大罵小三「騎別人的老公很爽是不是？」<br />\n名醫妻子還加碼爆料，老公有處女情結，高中時就立志當婦科醫師，因為這是找到處女的捷徑，還曾說因為她是處女所以喜歡她，看到處女的下體就會興奮，原本以為是玩笑話，後來發現老公喜歡找處女當小三，才知道是真的。<br />\n報導指出，名醫簽下離婚協議書後，與小三各付10萬元賠償金，也承諾放棄監護權，每個月支付8萬元生活費給老婆和子女，再與小三賠320萬元給妻子。但他後來又寄出存證信函，要求撤銷離婚協議，每月給2名子女各1萬元，其他的不願賠償。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/2747382\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F2747382&d=Ibp2r5avkWIk14HZtW%2BzJ6CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=1508457e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F2747382&h=9d4b392f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/2747382</a>"},{"pid":"9aff647cf9679d9b9d382c8c77d11f1bb7adf30a","tid":1092520,"uid":8131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:06:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MxtiDx0vhA4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMxtiDx0vhA4&d=Ibp2r5avkWIk14HZtW%2BzJ6CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=17bc263d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MxtiDx0vhA4</a>"},{"pid":"b03526046cf2901647626f1fc75da0b1ecc8f2dd","tid":1092520,"uid":63303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:07:14.000Z","msg":"苗粟+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b142a1f01e2aab93fb4bb2a149e51dcc8208ef","tid":1092520,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:08:13.000Z","msg":"I know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389c140cde855ce7312c3408869120369edd3396","tid":1092520,"uid":134226,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:09:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">老公有處女情結，高中時就立志當婦科醫師，因為這是找到處女的捷徑</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98990e1642a5601c383a5e05b7bf34d337ace442","tid":1092520,"uid":42253,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:11:17.000Z","msg":"正宮同小3 都好似好樣衰咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee604e992cbf75f238da493cfc28ef78d9007afd","tid":1092520,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:12:37.000Z","msg":"玩live咁痴線"},{"pid":"b1d0b8c3b49435cc90f8cebf8bb511ef963b5a8a","tid":1092520,"uid":95637,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"389c140cde855ce7312c3408869120369edd3396","tid":1092520,"uid":134226,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:09:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">老公有處女情結，高中時就立志當婦科醫師，因為這是找到處女的捷徑</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:12:56.000Z","msg":"有志者事竟成"},{"pid":"ae7934d7dd72dfd3ccb4281dc2664cb917fda9c2","tid":1092520,"uid":221790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:16:08.000Z","msg":"AV情節咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13bbd5d2c3ebf54c11e5f411a13f0779a8c6c13f","tid":1092520,"uid":116688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"